<template>
    <v-card>
        <v-toolbar class='blue-grey lighten-1 white--text font-weight-bold' dense flat>{{ this.foodTile }}
            <v-spacer></v-spacer>
            <template class='img'>
                <v-img :src='this.foodImage'></v-img>
            </template>
        </v-toolbar>
        <v-card-text class='py-4 my-2'>
            <slot></slot>
        </v-card-text>
    </v-card>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'FoodInformation',
    data() {
        return {
            foodTitle: "",
            foodImage: ""
        }
    },
    props: {
        foodName: String,
        foodImg: String
    },
    mounted() {
        this.foodTile = this.foodName
    },
}
</script>
